# Realbook Architecture Rules

## Core Philosophy
- Fastest stable MVP
- One feature at a time
- No overengineering
- Maintainable by future developers

## State Management
- Use React Context only
- No Zustand
- No Redux
- Local UI state stays local

## Services
- Screens never call Firebase directly
- All backend calls go through /src/services
- Keep services backend-agnostic

## Backend
- Firebase later
- AsyncStorage for MVP persistence
- Firestore structure must stay scalable

## Roles
- guest
- pending_agent
- verified_agent
- admin
- banned

## Product Rules
- Sale listings only
- No rentals in Phase 1
- Requirements not demands
- Record Room data never truly deleted
- CNIC admin-only
- Visiting card public

## Performance
- FlatList only for feeds
- Pagination required
- Optimize for Android mid-range phones
